# Input
```html
<!-- should generate diagnostics -->

<div class="ml-2 mr-2">Should be mx-2</div>

<div class="pl-2 pr-2 pt-2 pb-2">Should be p-2</div>

<div class="hover:w-4 hover:h-4">Should be hover:size-4</div>

<div class="border-x border-y">Should be border</div>

<div class="overflow-hidden text-ellipsis whitespace-nowrap">Should be truncate</div>

<div class="ml-2 mr-2 text-blue-500 font-bold">mx-2 should replace ml-2 mr-2</div>

<img class="mr-3 ml-3" src="example.png" alt="example" />

<div class='pt-1 pr-1 pb-1 pl-1'>Should be p-1</div>

<div class="border-x border-y overflow-hidden text-ellipsis whitespace-nowrap w-8 h-8">
  Multiple groups should compress: border, truncate, size-8
</div>

<div class="hover:w-10 hover:h-10 bg-gray-100 p-4">Should be hover:size-10</div>

<div class="-mt-2 -mb-2">Should be -my-2</div>

<div class="pl-6 pr-6 py-6">Should be px-6 py-6</div>

<!-- bugged, tailwind parser can't handle this -->
<!--<div class="  ml-4    mr-4   ">Whitespace should not prevent mx-4</div>-->

```

